OL,3,CThousands turn out for funeral of
OL,4,Cteenager who died at holiday park
OL,6,FThousands of people have turned out to
OL,7,Fpay their respects at the funeral of a
OL,8,Fteenage girl who died at a holiday
OL,9,Fpark.
OL,11,FCherish Bean, 15, and her boyfriend
OL,12,FEthan Slater, 17, were found dead in a
OL,13,Fcabin at Little Eden Holiday Park in
OL,14,FBridlington last month.
OL,16,FAn inquest at Hull Coroner's Court
OL,17,Fheard their deaths were suspected to
OL,18,Fhave been caused by carbon monoxide
OL,19,Fpoisoning.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
