OL,3,CThousands turn out for funeral of
OL,4,Cteenager who died at holiday park
OL,6,FOn Thursday, thousands gathered in
OL,7,FParson Cross to say their goodbyes as
OL,8,Fthe funeral procession made its way
OL,9,Ffrom Cherish's family home to St
OL,10,FMary's Church in Ecclesfield.
OL,12,FAlong the mile-long route, pink
OL,13,Fballoons were tied to lampposts and
OL,14,Frailings and flares were let off.
OL,16,FMourner Kayleigh Boldock said: "She
OL,17,Fwas a good friend of mine, she lit up
OL,18,Fevery single room that she went in,
OL,19,Fshe made the best out of everything,"
OL,20,Fshe said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774602329
OL,3,CThousands turn out for funeral of
OL,4,Cteenager who died at holiday park
OL,6,F"It's just devastating she's not here,
OL,7,Fyou've got no one to message in the
OL,8,Fmorning to brighten up your day.
OL,10,F"She was a young beautiful girl.Her
OL,11,Fmum and dad have done her proud. It's
OL,12,Fheartbreaking, we should be attending
OL,13,Fher 16th birthday, not her funeral at
OL,14,Fall."
OL,16,FFamily friend Deanna MacDonald said
OL,17,Feveryone in the community had been
OL,18,Faffected.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774602329
OL,3,CThousands turn out for funeral of
OL,4,Cteenager who died at holiday park
OL,6,F"She had so much to live for, she had
OL,7,Fthe best parents, she's absolutely
OL,8,Ftouched the hearts of everybody and
OL,9,Feverybody has come together," she said.
OL,11,FVicar, Reverend Dr Tim Gill said he
OL,12,Fhoped the response of the community
OL,13,Fwould bring comfort to the family.
OL,15,F"Sorry doesn't go far enough," he
OL,16,Fsaid. "The silent response of turning
OL,17,Fout, putting out the balloons and the
OL,18,Fribbons, they will know they're in the
OL,19,Fthoughts and hearts of the people of
OL,20,Fthis community."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
