FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774602329
OL,3,CThousands turn out for funeral of
OL,4,Cteenager who died at holiday park
OL,6,FAn inquest which opened into the
OL,7,Fcouple's deaths heard they had been on
OL,8,Fa family holiday and had both been
OL,9,F"fit and well" when the family spent
OL,10,Fthe evening together on 17 February.
OL,12,FSenior coroner Prof Paul Marks said
OL,13,FCherish left the family at about 9pm
OL,14,Ffor a smaller cabin, known as the "man
OL,15,Fcave", where she was staying with
OL,16,FEthan.
OL,18,FShe returned about an hour later
OL,19,Fcomplaining of a headache and later
OL,20,Fdied.
