OL,3,CThousands turn out for funeral of
OL,4,Cteenager who died at holiday park
OL,6,FFour people arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fgross negligence manslaughter in
OL,8,Fconnection with the teenagers' deaths
OL,9,Fremain on bail.
